In 1969 , Buzz Aldrin &apos;s historical step onto the moon leapt mankind into an era of technological possibility . The awesome power of technology was to be used to solve all of our big problems . Fast forward to present day , and what &apos;s happened ? Are mobile apps all we have to show for ourselves ? Journalist Jason Pontin looks closely at the challenges we face to using technology effectively ... for problems that really matter .
