&lt; description &gt; &quot; Babies and young children are like the R &amp; amp ; D division of the human species , &quot; says psychologist Alison Gopnik . Her research explores the sophisticated intelligence-gathering and decision-making that babies are really doing when they play . &lt; / description &gt;
