&lt; description &gt; A future more beautiful ? Architect Thomas Heatherwick shows five recent projects featuring ingenious bio-inspired designs . Some are remakes of the ordinary : a bus , a bridge , a power station ... And one is an extraordinary pavilion , the Seed Cathedral , a celebration of growth and light . &lt; / description &gt;
