&lt; description &gt; Every day there are news reports of new health advice , but how can you know if they &apos;re right ? Doctor and epidemiologist Ben Goldacre shows us , at high speed , the ways evidence can be distorted , from the blindingly obvious nutrition claims to the very subtle tricks of the pharmaceutical industry . &lt; / description &gt;
