I &apos;m used to thinking of the TED audience as a wonderful collection of some of the most effective , intelligent , intellectual , savvy , worldly and innovative people in the world .
And I think that &apos;s true .
However , I also have reason to believe that many , if not most , of you are actually tying your shoes incorrectly .
Now I know that seems ludicrous .
I know that seems ludicrous .
And believe me , I lived the same sad life until about three years ago .
And what happened to me was I bought , what was for me , a very expensive pair of shoes .
